    VCC       >>> 5V
    Yellow    >>> D8
    GND       >>> GND
  Based on: http://www.howmuchsnow.com/arduino/airquality/grovedust/
  Authors: Chris Nafis Apris 2012
  Datasheet:  http://www.sca-shinyei.com/pdf/PPD42NS.pdf
